agraph\" >在直播途中，VTuber會遇到各種突發事件，需要玩家按照女主角們的特性，提供合適的行動建議！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/217f5b85006555d8ab39b9cd839df366.avif?t=1769150542\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras_big/217f5b85006555d8ab39b9cd839df366.avif?t=1769150542 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/cafbbaeacc8e9c63518f2de2a0371d92.poster.avif?t=1769150542\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/cafbbaeacc8e9c63518f2de2a0371d92.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/cafbbaeacc8e9c63518f2de2a0371d92.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/617aa131f68afa906f6de6bcfc06bb1e.poster.avif?t=1769150542\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/617aa131f68afa906f6de6bcfc06bb1e.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/617aa131f68afa906f6de6bcfc06bb1e.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—時間管理大師—</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同步培養三位VTuber的你，需要好好分配行動點數，選擇見證哪位女主角的成長。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個培訓均安排了相應的小遊戲，表現出色時VTuber也能迅速成長！ </p><p class=\"bb_