3044740/extras/cafbbaeacc8e9c63518f2de2a0371d92.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/cafbbaeacc8e9c63518f2de2a0371d92.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/617aa131f68afa906f6de6bcfc06bb1e.poster.avif?t=1769150542\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/617aa131f68afa906f6de6bcfc06bb1e.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/617aa131f68afa906f6de6bcfc06bb1e.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>—時間管理大師—</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同步培養三位VTuber的你，需要好好分配行動點數，選擇見證哪位女主角的成長。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個培訓均安排了相應的小遊戲，表現出色時VTuber也能迅速成長！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【人物介紹】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/8a5b65cfeb94da114b6169e507e4c811.poster.avif?t=1769150542\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/8a5b65cfeb94da114b6169e507e4c811.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/8a5b65cfeb94da114b6169e507e4c811.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中之人名稱：黑沼唯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VTuber名稱：魅魔莉莉絲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：25歲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：180cm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罩杯：G</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：7月12日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陰沉內向的社恐宅女，直播時卻是格外奔放大膽的暴言系VTuber，渴望粉絲關注且重視互動的她養了不少真愛粉。本命是大山事務所的當紅VTuber犬山愛，憧憬著她的開朗與自信。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之所以有這樣自卑又孤僻的性格，是因為她深藏內心的某個事件。做愛時性格會變得格外強勢大膽，喜歡處於主導位置，也熱愛嘗試不同道具和場景……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/f27d204da1e3145603b74943cb47c839.poster.avif?t=1769150542\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/f27d204da1e3145603b74943cb47c839.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/f27d204da1e3145603b74943cb47c839.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中之人名稱：日向純子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VTuber名稱：花豹小葵  Hyou Aoi</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：21歲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：159cm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罩杯：F</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：8月20日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >陽光外向的大學新生辣妹。妹妹系雜談型VTuber，粉絲視她為療癒精神的小太陽，為了脫離不為人知的困境而進入事務所。  <br>不算很熟悉二次元文化，有時候會鬧出烏龍，所以很樂意被觀眾科普知識，不過有時會被別有用心地教導色色的事情。雖然外表是辣妹，但卻意外的非常清純？......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/2d0d2a7f7d4c1201bd0f26c858042b41.poster.avif?t=1769150542\" width=616 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/2d0d2a7f7d4c1201bd0f26c858042b41.webm?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/extras/2d0d2a7f7d4c1201bd0f26c858042b41.mp4?t=1769150542\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中之人名稱：井上早苗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VTuber名稱：修女特蕾莎 Sister Trisha</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >年齡：35歲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身高：166cm</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >罩杯：H</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生日：11月25日</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >認真笨拙的養成系VTuber，會認真回覆每位觀眾的留言和意見，獨特的人格魅力也吸引了不少愛操心的指示廚型粉絲，在不擅長的領域努力上進的性格讓人感動。縱然年紀已經不小，但為了實現往日的夢想而選擇成為VTuber。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看似生活安穩順遂的成熟人妻，但內心似乎因為某些原因而飽受煎熬。平日溫柔又認真的她，性慾其實非常強烈，渴望刺激又粗暴的性愛……</p>", "short_description": "陰差陽錯成為了VTuber事務所經紀人的你，肩負了培養三位VTuber重大使命。為了讓她們走上VTuber界的巔峰，不但需要悉心管理行程，還需要滿足她們的各種需♂求……！？目標是，培養出最能幹的VTuber！", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文<strong>*</strong>, 繁體中文<strong>*</strong>, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/5c64927906d8cac6eecd09f59ccf88df4a2168e9/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1769150542", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1769150542", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044740/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1769150542", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 560 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 10.3 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 760 / AMD Radeon HD 6870